{"tid":318211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港最後一間通心粉廠  第二代：超市入平價支那貨  我地冇錢賺都要繼續做","createTime":"2017-07-12T02:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T10:51:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":74,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f650d23f6c24a0b564bdd516dd8d34a297a7b38a","tid":318211,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:49:50.000Z","msg":"香港最後一間通心粉廠 第二代：冇錢賺都要繼續做<br />\n<br />\n通心粉肯定大家都吃過，不說不知，原來全港的通心粉廠只剩一家──「嘉齡食品」。皆因大部分食肆及超級市場都選擇入口平價的內地貨，而且製作過程繁複吃力，又賺不了大錢。工廠的第二代Calvin於2013年接手已運作四十餘年的通粉廠，為的，除了傳承父親的心血外，亦是以行動証明「來佬貨」不一定比本土產物來得香。<br />\n<br />\n嘉齡食品有限公司<br />\n地址：荃灣沙咀道45-53號荃運工業中心第1期1樓G室<br />\n電話：2411 0577<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_56920512/香港最後一間通心粉廠+第二代：冇錢賺都要繼續做/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetw.nextdigital.com.hk%2Farticle%2F3_56920512%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%80%E9%96%93%E9%80%9A%E5%BF%83%E7%B2%89%E5%BB%A0%2B%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%9A%E5%86%87%E9%8C%A2%E8%B3%BA%E9%83%BD%E8%A6%81%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E5%81%9A%2F1&d=tVQayoMpeeFv0KaNZAnvlsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=420a7127\" target=\"_blank\">https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_56920512/香港最後一間通心粉廠+第二代：冇錢賺都要繼續做/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://etw-image.nextdigital.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170706/large/1499313458_72e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetw-image.nextdigital.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170706%2Flarge%2F1499313458_72e3.jpg&h=cb41720e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://etw-image.nextdigital.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170706/large/1499313459_c48d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetw-image.nextdigital.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170706%2Flarge%2F1499313459_c48d.jpg&h=0f502994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://etw-image.nextdigital.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170706/large/1499313461_b1bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetw-